In Reitter’s collection at 
<collectionCode LSID="urn:lsid:biocol.org:col:34991" box="[569,662,1957,1983]" httpUri="http://biocol.org/urn:lsid:biocol.org:col:34991" name="Hungarian Natural History Museum (Termeszettudomanyi Muzeum)" pageId="15" pageNumber="16">HNHM</collectionCode>
, is a female (pinned through the right elytron which was cracked toward base of elytral humeri, elytra separated) bearing the handwritten labels: “Akbes”, “ 
<collectingCountry box="[1255,1324,1994,2020]" name="Syria" pageId="15" pageNumber="16">Syria</collectingCountry>
, Akbes”, “ 
<taxonomicName box="[164,392,152,177]" class="Insecta" family="Curculionidae" genus="Lixus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="convexicollis" status="n. sp.">
<emphasis box="[164,392,152,177]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">Lixus convexicollis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[400,465,152,178]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" rank="species">n. sp.</taxonomicNameLabel>
Petri”, “ 
<typeStatus box="[569,699,152,178]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">Holotypus</typeStatus>
, 
<number box="[711,773,152,178]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" value="1904.0">1904</number>
, 
<taxonomicName authority="Petri" authorityName="Petri" box="[786,1082,152,178]" class="Insecta" family="Curculionidae" genus="Lixus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="convexicollis">
<emphasis box="[786,1014,152,177]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">Lixus convexicollis</emphasis>
Petri
</taxonomicName>
” red brimmed museum label, and fitting the description with 
<typeStatus box="[523,574,189,215]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">type</typeStatus>
locality as Akbes, Caucasus, Araxes, and is here designated as 
<typeStatus box="[1328,1435,189,215]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">lectotype</typeStatus>
with “ 
<typeStatus box="[222,359,226,252]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">Lectotypus</typeStatus>
, Ƥ, 
<taxonomicName authority="Petri., Gultekin" authorityName="Petri., Gultekin" box="[410,828,226,252]" class="Insecta" family="Curculionidae" genus="Lixus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="convexicollis">
<emphasis box="[410,637,226,251]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">Lixus convexicollis</emphasis>
Petri., Gültekin
</taxonomicName>
des. 
<number box="[890,954,226,252]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" value="2008.0">2008</number>
”, “ 
<taxonomicName authority="Boh., Gultekin" authorityName="Boh., Gultekin" box="[991,1385,226,252]" class="Insecta" family="Curculionidae" genus="Lixus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="elegantulus">
<emphasis box="[991,1201,226,251]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">Lixus elegantulus</emphasis>
Boh., Gültekin
</taxonomicName>
det. 
<number box="[151,216,264,290]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" value="2008.0">2008</number>
”.
</paragraph>
